# ==========================================================================
# > 拼多多（PDD）纯分流广告与视频拦截流（不折腾/无解密/稳定版）
# > 专属定制：Hubfilter / QuantumultX
# ==========================================================================

# > 1. 拦截“多多视频”流及视频缓存（让视频页彻底瘫痪、无法加载）
HOST-KEYWORD, pddvideo, REJECT
HOST-SUFFIX, pddvideo.pinduoduo.com, REJECT
HOST-SUFFIX, video.yangkeduo.com, REJECT

# > 2. 拦截拼多多的追踪、日志上报及广告统计（减少后台小动作和摇一摇广告）
HOST, t-track.pinduoduo.com, REJECT
HOST, track.pinduoduo.com, REJECT
HOST, log.pinduoduo.com, REJECT
HOST, stat.pinduoduo.com, REJECT
HOST, analytics.pinduoduo.com, REJECT

# > 3. 拦截拼多多的弹窗、营销下发和广告位资源
HOST, api.xunmeng.pinduoduo.com, REJECT
HOST, amdc.m.taobao.com, REJECT
HOST, amdc.alipay.com, REJECT

# > 4. 拼多多正常购物、支付、看订单流量放行（走直连，不影响日常使用）
HOST-KEYWORD, pinduoduo, DIRECT
HOST-KEYWORD, yangkeduo, DIRECT
HOST-SUFFIX, pinduoduo.com, DIRECT
HOST-SUFFIX, yangkeduo.com, DIRECT
